---
// InstallIOSGuide.astro
---
<div class="space-y-4 text-sm font-medium">
  <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 sm:gap-4 sm:p-4 rounded-2xl" style="background: rgba(128,128,128,0.1);">
    <div class="w-6 h-6 shrink-0 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] shadow-sm mt-0.5" style="background: var(--brand-nav-icon-active, #f59e0b);">1</div>
    <p style="color: var(--brand-nav-text, #d1d5db); display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; gap: 0.25rem;" class="leading-relaxed">
      Toca el botón <svg class="inline-block w-5 h-5 -mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 12v8a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-8"></path><polyline points="16 6 12 2 8 6"></polyline><line x1="12" y1="2" x2="12" y2="15"></line></svg> <strong>Compartir</strong> en la barra de Safari
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 sm:gap-4 sm:p-4 rounded-2xl" style="background: rgba(128,128,128,0.1);">
    <div class="w-6 h-6 shrink-0 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] shadow-sm mt-0.5" style="background: var(--brand-nav-icon-active, #f59e0b);">2</div>
    <p style="color: var(--brand-nav-text, #d1d5db); display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; gap: 0.25rem;" class="leading-relaxed">
      Desliza y selecciona <svg class="inline-block w-5 h-5 -mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="4" ry="4"></rect><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="16"></line><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"></line></svg> <strong>Añadir a pantalla de inicio,</strong> quizás debas tocar en <strong>Ver más</strong>
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 sm:gap-4 sm:p-4 rounded-2xl" style="background: rgba(128,128,128,0.1);">
    <div class="w-6 h-6 shrink-0 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold text-[var(--text-primary)] shadow-sm" style="background: var(--brand-nav-icon-active, #f59e0b);">3</div>
    <p style="color: var(--brand-nav-text, #d1d5db);" class="leading-relaxed mt-0.5">Toca <strong>Añadir</strong> en la esquina superior derecha</p>
  </div>
</div>
